channel.title: Do you think this about Jagex?
channel.description:
Hey, what's up? I was just thinking...For awhile now...
Do any of you think that Jagex would actually send out one of their employee's, or hire someone to go on a RSPS to see what we are up to? IDK, Maybe i'm just being paranoid -.- but i've been thinking that for awhile now.
What do you think?
